{"tid":2390154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩男生驅散期間奔跑被控非法集結 辯方指二人主動停下讓警查證","createTime":"2021-02-01T11:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T13:53:47.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5ecead440b007bf9cafe3b079776ada263c332","tid":2390154,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:04:48.000Z","msg":"前年11月11日市民發起全港三罷「黎明行動」，有示威者疑於油麻地堵路，其後警方到場進行驅散，並以非法集結罪拘捕兩名18歲男學生。案件今於九龍城法院開審，警員供稱當時有示威者於馬路堵路，<span class=\"red\">驅散時看見兩名被告逃跑，遂上前截停他們</span>。辯方指兩被告遭警員喝止後，主動停下腳步，又聽從指示向警方出示身份證。<br />\n<br />\n蕭另被控於同日同地攜有一個能發出雷射光束的裝置。案件由裁判官<span class=\"red\">鄭念慈</span>審理。<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問時指出，<span class=\"red\">警員13129鍾耀進</span>追截二人至砵蘭街期間，必定曾移開注視二人的視線，而兩被告是被警員喝止而主動停下腳步。鍾不同意辯方的說法，惟鍾坦言兩被告聽從警方的指示，拿出身份證讓警方調查。"},{"pid":"772fda23a994264f7be5b8b50cd58aa7f84847d4","tid":2390154,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/NFZHVHME4VAEVB72Z7QRLDUNPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FNFZHVHME4VAEVB72Z7QRLDUNPU%2F&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=051c01a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FNFZHVHME4VAEVB72Z7QRLDUNPU%2F&h=5256b165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/NFZHVHME4VAEVB72Z7QRLDUNPU/</a>"},{"pid":"aa57123a463575aa2fb03fad937cc1a158cef77a","tid":2390154,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d40e6e15896b4c9f7cced5001ae8518d5f02fa9","tid":2390154,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"鍾看到兩名身穿灰色上衣、揹上背囊的被告「跑跑下突然變咗行」，遂展開追捕，終於砵蘭街的國際夜總會外擒獲兩人，並交由另外兩警作搜查，自己則在旁守候及戒備。<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問時指出，鍾追截兩人期間曾移開視線，兩名被告因聽到警員警告，而主動停下腳步。鍾不同意，但承認兩被告聽從警方的指示，拿出身分證。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-11-%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%B7-%E5%85%A9%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E5%8F%97%E5%AF%A9-%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E8%81%BD%E5%BE%9E%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AD%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-11-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BD%25B7-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E8%2581%25BD%25E5%25BE%259E%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%2F&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=390eb07a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-11-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BD%25B7-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E8%2581%25BD%25E5%25BE%259E%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%2F&h=4552fe78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-11-%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%B7-%E5%85%A9%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E5%8F%97%E5%AF%A9-%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E8%81%BD%E5%BE%9E%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E5%87